"{\n  \"text\": \"I wanted to make a quick video about the garden today at my house. We've had a wonderful early fall, and it's uh or I guess late fall, I'm thinking about, but it's uh temperatures have gone down nicely, and behind me are a couple of the pitched piles that I do to make our fine soil. That's the later one, and that one right there is the most recent one. Uh coming over here is our aerated static pile, which is getting on about two and a half weeks old. Um it's predominantly cooled down. Um pretty sunny. Uh and this is the fan and the pipes and the pile. It's pretty good size, but it's shrank quite a bit as compost piles will do as they begin to break down. Um here's the chicken tractor. And there's one of the girls getting a little bit of water. That's great. I love chicken, they're so much fun. Uh this is the garden we've been working on. Um and there's quite a few more beds as you can see. And uh some of this is just getting going. Uh mostly it's fall stuff, so it's gonna be roots and lettuces, carrots, potatoes, uh, radishes, beets, things like that, and a bunch of different lettuces of all different types. But you can see we have uh let's see, 12 beds now, and most of them are beginning to spring up. We just planted these uh yesterday, and the ones over in the background we planted a couple days ago, about a week ago, and it's all coming up beautifully. Door slammed on the chicken coop. It's a little bit windy today, uh, but a gorgeous day, and uh we're super excited about this garden, and uh thanks a lot, y'all. Take it easy.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" I wanted to make a quick video about the garden today at my house.\",\n      \"start\": 0.24,\n      \"end\": 5.04,\n      \"duration\": 4.8,\n      \"confidence\": 0.994,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" I\",\n          \"start\": 0.24,\n          \"end\": 0.48,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.997\n        },\n        {\n  